node.text:
It's hard to believe that just a month ago I was having a great time pulling shots of espresso and helping out around The Fuel Shack. I've been drafted into the COVID 19 effort and I'm glad to do my part. 
California's peak of infections will be here in a week or so, so it's time to double down on our efforts to slow the spread. Of course wash your hands, of course wear a mask in public, and most importantly, STAY HOME as much as you can. 
Before you know it, we'll be back hanging out and laughing at The Fuel Shack, but until then, please take this seriously and do your part! Stay well, we love you all, and we'll see you soon ‚ù£Ô∏è‚ù£Ô∏èüôèüèΩ
.
.
.
.
.
#thefuelshack #fuelforyoursoul #fuelupfeelgood #foodcoffeelove #lovealways #covid_19 #stayhome #staysafe #flattenthecurve

node.text:
To our beautiful community: first, we love you, and we miss you like crazy. Although I think our finely crafted espresso drinks and amazing food are essential, we didn't feel like staying open, even in a take-out and delivery mode was the right thing to do for us. 
But coffee IS essential, and our friends at Campos Coffee @camposcoffeeusa have arranged to have their award-winning coffee shipped to you with minimal hassle and maximum joy (and flavor)! I'll leave a link in our bio. Use the code FUELSHACK2 for free shipping and get your coffee game on point again! 
We'll see you again soon, but in the meantime, please be careful and please do your part to keep us all safe and healthy! ‚ù£Ô∏è‚ù£Ô∏è‚ù£Ô∏è
.
.
.
.

node.text:
It can be frustrating not knowing how to help in situations like we're facing. Here's one small way that can have a big impact: if you have extra face masks, gloves, gowns, face shields or other Personal Protective Equipment, consider donating them to protect our front line health care workers! Check out the details on the flyer...
.
PS if you've had any relatives on home health, check out the box of supplies they almost always leave behind. You might find some of these items...
.
.
.
.
#covid_19 #covid #flatteningthecurve #flattenthecurve

I don't have a coffee machine at home, so I came down to the Shack and fired up the La Marzocco, ground the beautiful @camposcoffeeusa beans and made my morning almond milk flat white with nephew Greg. Greg is helping us update our website and get our online ordering/payment/delivery thing going. Stay tuned.... Much love to all of you. Stay healthy and continue to vibrate at a high frequency! ‚ù£Ô∏èüôèüèΩ
